snippet.title: WHO'S WHO 2.0 | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
🔗Game link: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3391260/WHOS_WHO_20/

Description:
WHO'S WHO 2.0 is back with a brand new team! This dynamic party game introduces unique character skills that impact each mode with distinct advantages. Play solo or with friends, and become the winner by eliminating real players hidden among NPCs. Released on March 21, 2025.
